											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player wakes up in the dream field. Shot of the Emperor is sitting with its back to you on a bench, alone, looking unusually pensive and morose against the backdrop of the astral plane - the globe of domination visible in the distance. All is quiet now in contrast to the battles we previously saw here. The player approaches." />
